WEBVTT

00:00:01.400 --> 00:00:02.616
Hello.

00:00:02.640 --> 00:00:04.576
My name is Matthew Williams,

00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:06.520
and I am a champion.

00:00:07.520 --> 00:00:10.376
I have won medals
in three different sports

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:13.136
and national games in Canada,

00:00:13.160 --> 00:00:16.656
competed at the international
level in basketball

00:00:16.680 --> 00:00:19.736
and was proud to represent Canada

00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:21.376
on the world stage.

00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:25.680
(Applause)

00:00:27.040 --> 00:00:31.256
I train five days a week
for basketball and speed skating,